column5: On the whole, I am not satisfied with myself.
column6: At times, I think I am no good at all.
column7: I feel that I don't have a good number of qualities.
column8: I am not able to do things as well as most other people.
column9: I feel I do not have much to be proud of.
column10: I certainly feel useless at times.
column11: I feel that I am not a person of worth, at least not even on an equal plane with others.
column12: I don't like to respect myself
column13: All in all, I am inclined to think that I am a failure.
column14: I do not take a positive attitude towards myself.
